# RPG Systems: Stats & Skills Comparison

## Primary Attributes

| Attribute Concept | AD&D (1e/2e) | Rolemaster (RMSS) | DSA (4.1/5) | GURPS (4e) | Call of Cthulhu (7e) |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Physical Strength | Strength (STR) | Strength (St) | Körperkraft (KK) | Strength (ST) | Strength (STR) |
| Agility/Dexterity | Dexterity (DEX) | Agility (Ag) | Gewandtheit (GE) | Dexterity (DX) | Dexterity (DEX) |
| Endurance/Health | Constitution (CON) | Constitution (Co) | Konstitution (KO) | Health (HT) | Constitution (CON) |
| Intelligence | Intelligence (INT) | Reasoning (Re) | Klugheit (KL) | Intelligence (IQ) | Intelligence (INT) |
| Willpower/Wisdom | Wisdom (WIS) | Self Discipline (SD) | Mut (MU) | Will (Will) | Power (POW) |
| Social/Charisma | Charisma (CHA) | Presence (Pr) | Charisma (CH) | — (advantages) | Appearance (APP) |
| Perception | — (WIS subsumes) | — (skill-based) | Intuition (IN) | Perception (Per) | — (skill-based) |
| Speed/Quickness | — (DEX subsumes) | Quickness (Qu) | — (derived) | Basic Speed (derived) | — (derived MOV) |
| Memory/Learning | — | Memory (Me) | — | — | — |
| Empathy | — | Empathy (Em) | — | — | — |
| Intuition | — | Intuition (In) | Intuition (IN) | — | — |
| Finger dexterity | — | — | Fingerfertigkeit (FF) | — | — |
| Courage | — (roleplayed) | — | Mut (MU) | — | — |
| **Range** | **3–18** (3d6) | **1–102** (open-ended) | **1–21** (typical 8–14) | **1–20** (10 = average) | **15–90** (3d6×5) |
| **Total # of attrs** | **6** | **10** | **8** | **4 primary + 2 secondary** | **7** (+ derived) |

### DSA 5e full attribute list
MU (Mut/Courage), KL (Klugheit/Cunning), IN (Intuition), CH (Charisma), FF (Fingerfertigkeit/Dexterity), GE (Gewandtheit/Agility), KO (Konstitution), KK (Körperkraft/Strength)

### Rolemaster full attribute list
St (Strength), Co (Constitution), Ag (Agility), Qu (Quickness), SD (Self Discipline), Re (Reasoning), Me (Memory), Pr (Presence), In (Intuition), Em (Empathy)

