## Derived Stats

| Concept | AD&D | Rolemaster | DSA | GURPS | CoC 7e |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Hit Points | HP (class HD + CON) | Hits (Co-based) | Lebensenergie (LE) | Hit Points (ST+HT) | Hit Points (CON+SIZ)/10 |
| Magic/Mana | Spell slots (class) | Power Points (realm stat) | Astralenergie (AE) | Fatigue Points (FP) | Magic Points (POW/5) |
| Defense | AC (armor + DEX) | DB (Defensive Bonus) | Parade/Ausweichen | Dodge / Parry / Block | Dodge (DEX/2) |
| Initiative | d10 + modifiers | +Qu bonus | INI (MU+GE)/2 + d6 | Basic Speed | DEX |
| Movement | Race-based (12/9/6) | BMR (Qu/St) | Geschwindigkeit (GE) | Basic Move (Speed×1) | MOV |
| Fatigue/Endurance | — | Exhaustion Points | Ausdauer (AU) in 4.1 | Fatigue Points (HT) | — |
| Sanity | — | — | — | Fright Check | Sanity (POW×5) |
| Luck | — | — | — | — | Luck (3d6×5) |
| Wound threshold | — | Critical thresholds | Wundschwelle (KO/2) | Shock (HT) | Major Wound (HP/2) |

---

## Skill Systems Overview

| Aspect | AD&D | Rolemaster | DSA | GURPS | CoC 7e |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Mechanic** | d20 ≤ ability or THAC0 | d100 open-ended + skill ranks + stat bonuses | 3d20 vs 3 attrs + skill | 3d6 ≤ skill | d100 ≤ skill% |
| **Stat integration** | Single ability check | 2–3 stat bonuses per skill category | 3 attrs per talent | Single controlling attr | Single stat × multiplier |
| **# of Skills** | ~30 (NWP, 2e) | ~200+ in ~40 categories | ~59 talents + ~50 spells | ~250+ (open list) | ~40+ |
| **Skill grouping** | By ability score | Skill categories (develop category + individual skill) | By attribute group (DSA5: combat/physical/social/nature/knowledge/craft) | By controlling attribute | Broad categories |
| **Advancement** | Level-based (slots) | Dev. Points → category ranks + skill ranks per level | AP → skill points | Character points → skill | Skill check marks / free study |
| **Default** | Ability check | No rank = −25 penalty | Untrained = attr check | IQ/DX/etc − penalty | Base% |
| **Critical** | Nat 20 / Nat 1 | Open-ended roll (96+) | Double 1s / Double 20s | Crit on 3-4 / Fumble 17-18 | 01 / 100 |

---

## Skill Categories

### Combat Skills

| Category | AD&D | Rolemaster | DSA | GURPS | CoC |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Melee weapon | THAC0 + WP slots | Weapon skill (by type) | AT/PA per weapon | Weapon skill (e.g. Broadsword) | Fighting (Brawl) |
| Ranged weapon | THAC0 + WP slots | Weapon skill (by type) | FK per weapon | Weapon skill (e.g. Bow) | Firearms (Handgun) |
| Unarmed | Punching/Wrestling table | Martial Arts (various) | Raufen | Brawling / Karate / Judo | Fighting (Brawl) |
| Dodge/Parry | AC / class-based | DB (adrenal dodge) | Ausweichen | Dodge (DX-based) | Dodge |
| Armor use | Class restriction | Armor skill (by type) | Implicit in AT/PA | No skill (DR from armor) | — |
| Shield | AC bonus | Shield skill | Schildkampf | Shield (Block) | — |

